      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried some acetaminophen earlier but it wasnt really doing much for the pain. i really need something that actually works so i can get some sleep. if i just take a single standard dose of ibuprofen, is it really gonna be that big of a deal? i dont have any other bleeding issues or anything.",
